column16: Matt Szczur lines out softly to second baseman Ivan De Jesus.
Javier Baez grounds into a double play, pitcher Matt Magill to second baseman Ivan De Jesus to first baseman Joey Votto.   Miguel Montero out at 2nd.
Jhonny Peralta homers (8) on a fly ball to center field.   Randal Grichuk scores.    Stephen Piscotty scores.
Yadier Molina pops out to first baseman Joey Votto in foul territory.
Randal Grichuk singles on a line drive to left fielder Adam Duvall.   Matt Carpenter to 2nd.
Javier Baez pops out to second baseman Brandon Phillips.
Jason Heyward singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Scott Schebler.   Ben Zobrist to 3rd.
Ben Zobrist flies out to left fielder Adam Duvall.
Anthony Rizzo grounds into a double play, second baseman Brandon Phillips to shortstop Jose Peraza to first baseman Joey Votto.   Dexter Fowler to 3rd.    Kris Bryant out at 2nd.
Kris Bryant singles on a line drive to left fielder Adam Duvall.   Dexter Fowler to 2nd.
Dexter Fowler singles on a soft fly ball to center fielder Tyler Holt.
David Freese grounds out sharply, pitcher Matt Magill to first baseman Joey Votto.
Jordy Mercer pops out to second baseman Tony Renda on the infield fly rule.
Eric Fryer out on a sacrifice bunt, catcher Ramon Cabrera to first baseman Joey Votto.   Adam Frazier to 2nd.
